:: Functions
# window.story Functions

Here are some core Snowman 1.X functions in action:

<% 
  // Show current story state
  print("<p><strong>Story name:</strong> " + window.story.name + "</p>");
  print("<p><strong>Current passage:</strong> " + window.story.passage + "</p>");
  print("<p><strong>History length:</strong> " + window.story.history.length + "</p>");
%>

**Available passages:** 
<%
  const passages = Object.keys(window.story.passages);
  print("<ul>");
  passages.forEach(function(name) {
    print("<li>" + name + "</li>");
  });
  print("</ul>");
%>

[[See passage content->PassageContent]]
